OL,3,CNI Winter Fuel payments to end for
OL,4,Csome pensioners
OL,6,FStormont's Communities Minister Gordon
OL,7,FLyons has confirmed that a move to end
OL,8,Fthe winter fuel allowance to some
OL,9,Fpensioners will be extended to
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FIt was confirmed on Friday afternoon
OL,13,Fthe payment will be cut for pensioners
OL,14,Fin Northern Ireland who are not
OL,15,Freceiving means-tested benefits.
OL,17,FIt comes after similar changes were
OL,18,Fmade to the Winter Fuel Payments in
OL,19,FEngland and Wales last month.
