OL,3,CNI Winter Fuel payments to end for
OL,4,Csome pensioners
OL,6,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons
OL,7,Fsaid: "On 29 July 2024 the Chancellor
OL,8,Fof the Exchequer announced that
OL,9,Fentitlement to Winter Fuel Payments in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales would be restricted
OL,11,Fto those people receiving Pension
OL,12,FCredit or other means-tested benefits
OL,13,Fonly.
OL,15,F"I strongly disagree with this
OL,16,Fdecision.
