OL,3,CNI Winter Fuel payments to end for
OL,4,Csome pensioners
OL,6,F"The estimated additional cost to the
OL,7,FBlock Grant of maintaining universal
OL,8,Fentitlement to a Winter Fuel Payment
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland for Winter 2024/25
OL,10,Fis #44.3million, and this does not
OL,11,Finclude any additional delivery or
OL,12,Fstaffing costs.
OL,14,F"Regrettably, there is no additional
OL,15,Fresource available in the budget to
OL,16,Fallow us to diverge from the UK
OL,17,FGovernment decision without
OL,18,Fsignificantly cutting other public
OL,19,Fservices.
