OL,3,CNI Winter Fuel payments to end for
OL,4,Csome pensioners
OL,6,F"I have made clear to the Secretary of
OL,7,FState for Work and Pensions my total
OL,8,Fopposition to this decision and
OL,9,Foutlined the detrimental impact it
OL,10,Fwill have on many people in Northern
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,F"I am committed to ensuring that
OL,14,Fpeople can access all the support to
OL,15,Fwhich they are entitled and would
OL,16,Fencourage anyone affected by these
OL,17,Fchanges to check their benefit
OL,18,Fentitlement.
